(149, 1, '2018-09-22 11:23:23', '2018-09-22 18:23:23', '<label> Your Name (required)\r\n    [text* your-name] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Your Email (required)\r\n    [email* your-email] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Subject\r\n    [text your-subject] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Your Message\r\n    [textarea your-message] </label>\r\n\r\n<label> Submit your work. PDF, PNG or JPG. 8MB maximum file size.\r\n[file file-946 limit:8mb filetypes:pdf|jpg|png id:foo class:bar]\r\n</label>\r\n\r\n[submit \"Send\"]\n1\nSoundblog_Plugins \"[your-subject]\"\n[your-name] <wordpress@localhost>\nmwilson@nic.bc.ca\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Soundblog_Plugins (http://localhost:8888)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n[file-946]\n\n\n\nSoundblog_Plugins \"[your-subject]\"\nSoundblog_Plugins <wordpress@localhost>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on Soundblog_Plugins (http://localhost:8888)\nReply-To: mwilson@nic.bc.ca\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'Contact About page', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2018-09-24 08:13:18', '2018-09-24 15:13:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=149', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
(150, 1, '2018-09-22 11:25:31', '2018-09-22 18:25:31', '<h5>Megan Wilson</h5>\r\nVestibulum at enim in ante varius commodo in eget magna. Fusce nulla ipsum, blandit nec tortor non, vestibulum finibus elit. Nam fringilla tristique quam, et sodales dui laoreet at. Sed est mi, rhoncus nec scelerisque a, mollis in ante. Fusce volutpat augue est, in ornare orci eleifend nec. Maecenas a blandit sem. Phasellus vitae finibus lectus. Fusce eu accumsan sapien. Maecenas ornare ac erat et tristique. Aliquam sit amet lacus justo. Integer at neque gravida, laoreet nisl non, viverra mi.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_92\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/about-the-author/sophie-calle/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-92\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-92\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Sophie-Calle-300x296.jpg\" alt=\"author photograph\" width=\"300\" height=\"296\" /></a> Megan Wilson is the author of this blog[/caption]\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"149\" title=\"Contact About page\"]', 'About the Author', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-22 11:25:31', '2018-09-22 18:25:31', '', 73, 'http://localhost:8888/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
